snippet.title: Sable gameplay developer presentation - Future Games Show Gamescom
snippet.description:
Subscribe to Gamesradar: http://goo.gl/cnjsn1
Sable is an open-world exploration game with echoes of Ico and Journey. Announced to much acclaim in 2018, here's your first proper look at the gameplay, as our hero wrestles with her destiny in an ancient land. Due on current gen consoles, Xbox Series X and PC in 2020.
